  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6770.78 sitting between the massive negative gamma wall at 6760 (-48B) and positive gamma clusters above, dealers are currently in buy-the-dip mode while approaching the amplifying zone. The regime flip to PIN with 79B total GEX creates a strong mean-reversion setup where dealers will aggressively sell any push toward the 6800 max positive gamma level (+65B) while providing support above 6760. Key inflection points are 6760 (dealer buying accelerates below) and 6800 (dealer selling pressure peaks), with the 6807 flip strike acting as the regime boundary.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6760-6800 with dealers fighting moves outside this range.",
